---
title: Pan Seared Garlic Chicken with Crispy Broccoli and Potatoes Huancaina
description: Potatoes huancaína is a traditional Peruvian side dish consisting of Yukon potatoes smothered in a cheesy sauce. Cream cheese is our secret ingredient to making this drizzly, citrusy sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-seared-garlic-chicken-916bde7c.jpg
